Hasna Benhassi (Arabic; amụrụ na abalị mbu, na onwa isii, na afọ 1978) bụ onye Morocco lara ezumike nká na-agba ọsọ n'etiti
O sonyere na 2000, 2004 na 2008 Olympics ma merie ihe nrite abụọ na 800m, na 2004 na 2008
Na asọmpi ụwa, o ritere ihe nrite ọla edo karịa 1500 m n'ime ụlọ na 2001 na ihe nrite ego karịa 800 m n'èzí na 2005 na 2007
N'afọ 2004, a kpọrọ ya onye egwuregwu nke Afọ na Morocco mgbe nyocha nke Moroccan Radio mere n'etiti ụlọ ọrụ mgbasa ozi 43.
Benhassi lụrụ onye na-agba ọsọ n'etiti etiti nke Olympic Mouhssin Chehibi; ha nwere nwa nwanyị aha ya bụ Farah.
